ttp_template:
<group name="auth_key_auth_protocol_priv_key_priv_protocol">
 user-version  {{VERSION | ORPHRASE}}
 auth-protocol {{AUTH_PROTOCOL | ORPHRASE}}
 priv-protocol {{PRIV_PROTOCOL | ORPHRASE}}
snmp user {{USERNAME | ORPHRASE}}
 user-group  {{USER_GROUP | ORPHRASE}}
 auth-key  {{AUTH_KEY | ORPHRASE}}
</group>
